sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor Client
  participant API as Gateway
  participant RL as Rate Limiter
  participant App as Backend App

  Client->>API: GET /reports
  API->>RL: Check token quota
  alt Within quota
    RL-->>API: Allow
    API->>App: Forward request
    App-->>API: Response payload
    API-->>Client: 200 OK
  else Quota exceeded
    RL-->>API: Block
    API-->>Client: 429 Too Many Requests
  end
